    <aside>
    üí° Try link as email, image, button (`~~href~~ ‚Üí onclick=‚Äù‚Äù`) v√† g·∫Øn
    
    </aside>
    
- Style width & height
    1. Attribute width: `<a width=‚Äù500‚Äù>`
    2. Attribute CSS: `<a style=‚Äùwidth:500px‚Äù>`
    
    Ngo√†i ra c√≤n `style=‚Äùfloat:left‚Äù` (ƒë·∫©y ·∫£nh sang tr√°i ph·∫£i c·ªßa text)
    
