    - Trong Flex container la flex items, ngo√†i ƒë·ªëng tr√™n c√≤n
        - Cho Flex container
            - flex-wrap: nowrap, wrap, wrap, reverse
            - align-content: stretch, ‚Ä¶(nh∆∞ align-items, khi c√≥ flex: wrap: wrap)
        - Cho Flex items
            - align-self: auto ho·∫∑c nh∆∞ align-item ‚Üí t·ª± align ch√≠nh n√≥, t√°ch kh·ªèi container nhg vx ·ªü trong container
            - `flex-grow`
            - flex-basis ‚Üí l√†m m·ªçi flex items m·ªôt k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc n√†o ƒë√≥, vd 100px width n·∫øu c√°i g√¨ to h∆°n th√¨ fix v·ªÅ 100px, b√© h∆°n th√¨ grow ra ‚Üí nhg kp n√≥ s·∫Ω theo m√† tu·ª≥ setup container ho·∫∑c screen ‚Üí d√πng flex-shrink th√¨ n√≥ m·ªõi nguy√™n
                - chia 5 v√≠ d·ª• 2 c·ªôt trong flex div set c·ªôt tr√°i `flex-basis: 40%`
            - `flex-shrink` ‚Üí ki·ªÉu nh∆∞ nowrap khi ƒë·∫∑t trong flex m√† b·ªã wrap (ph√° constraint autolayout)
            - order: 0/1/-1 (-1=first, 1=last)
            - grid-column: 1 / -1
            - el‚Äî4
