## ************************Responsive web design************************

Element- > component ‚Üí layout ‚Üí page 

Work on all browser

- -ms: microsoft
- -moz: mozilla
- -webkit: chrom, safari

Fluid layout = adapt to curent view p·ªèt ‚Üí `%, vh, vw > px` and `max-width > width`

Responsive ‚Üí rem + imgae in max-width and % + media queries

10px = 0.625rem = 62.5%

### Components

Modal, forms, tables, logo, steps, tabs, breadcrumbs, nav, footer, sidebar, pagination (d√£y s·ªë), input, tags‚Ä¶‚Üí like Figma

### 7 steps to solve problems

1. Define
    1. About: what is all about = short brief
        1. Who use: client
        2. What for 
            1. Business goal: *selling diet plan* 
            2. User goal: *diet plan? ‚Üí subscribe monthly 1 meal/day (action) =  eat well effortlessly without spending time (desired state)*
        3. Target user: *busy but wealthy people, techgie*
2. Plan 
    1. Content
        1. Need sitemap? 
        2. Summary *‚Üí ~mission & description of the business*
        3. Features
        4. *How it works, Benefits, Samples, Copies, Pricing, Contact‚Ä¶*
        5. Links and layout requirements: *signup, login, ios app, android app, For enterprise, Hiring, Partnership, Press, Help center, Privacy and terms‚Ä¶*
    2. Visual asset
    3. Personality
3. Structure and Sketch 
    1. Page 1 = Home
        1. Header
        2. Hero
        3. Featured
        4. How it works 
        5. Meals + Diets
        6. Testimonials + Gallery
        7. Pricing + Features
        8. CTA
        9. Footer
    2. Page 2, 3, 4‚Ä¶
    
    ‚áí each section i, ii, iv‚Ä¶ = 1 mood board with different layouts
    
    ‚áí combine & SKETCH ideas
    
    ![Untitled](WEB101x%20-%20Build%20your%20first%20website%2030ff11bcca8542a6a32c1c20b077aa14/Untitled%2024.png)
    
4. CODE
    1. Structure folder
    2. Code layout (ch√∫ th√≠ch trong sketch)
        1. Nh·ªõ comment chia sections HTML + branding CSS
            
            ![Untitled](WEB101x%20-%20Build%20your%20first%20website%2030ff11bcca8542a6a32c1c20b077aa14/Untitled%2025.png)
            

